                <h1>Easy Guide to Applying Peel and Stick Wallpaper</h1>
                <p>Putting up peel and stick wallpaper is a fun, easy way to transform any space without the mess of traditional wallpaper. Begin by selecting a smooth surface and measuring your wall for a perfect fit. Peel off the backing, align the wallpaper, and stick it on. Use a smoothing tool to eliminate bubbles for a flawless finish.</p>
